string.name: helpContentHhml
string.Data:
1. You can set the time to start or stop the airplane mode. You can add more than one tasks.

    2. When the time is up(maybe there is a several minutes delay), this App attempted to switch(start or stop) the airplane mode with your permission(You\'d better add this App to the authorized list, or else it will ask for permission every time)

    3. When the time is up and you are using the device at the same time, you\'ll have 5 seconds to consider switch it right now or not. It will switch into the airplane mode if you do not take any action.

    4. Click the menu item "Operation logs" to view the details of operations. You can clear it when the log is too many.

    5. Feel free to contact me if you have any questions：tanglei\'s blog

string.name: helpContentHhml
string.Data:
1.分别设定好需要开启、关闭飞行模式的时间，点击某个任务状态的按钮会提示该任务下次执行的时间。您可以一次性设置多个任务。

    2.设定的时间到之后(根据设备运行状态可能有不同时间的延迟)，App会自动尝试去启用飞行模式状态，当然得允许了(最好添加到信任程序列表，不然每次弹框)。

    3.设定的时间到之后，有可能你还正在使用手机而不想马上切换飞行模式，App会给你5s的时间考虑，5秒之后你没有操作，App就会自动启用飞行模式了。你可以点击取消终止本次操作。

    4.点击菜单“查看运行日志”可以查看App的运行操作的记录，当日志过多时，您可以选择清空。

    5.更多图文教程请访问：tanglei\'s blog
